title: Rookie Competition + Superflex Strategy, Toilet Time - Fantasy Football Podcast for 7/9
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, a number of tough questions answered! Will rookie RBs compete for touches with Rashaad Penny or Austin Ekeler? DJ Moore or Terry McLaurin in 2022? Plus, Jason and Mike give their tips for 2QB / superflex leagues! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for July 9th, 2022.

The 2022 Ultimate Draft Kit and Draft Analyzer are available NOW
